{"tid":772601,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 被其他apps認左做Jailbroken device","createTime":"2018-08-09T01:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T08:04:30.000Z","uid":3894,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb33995a5af931caf6fed375fbbf8b2aa34849e","tid":772601,"uid":3894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:51:23.000Z","msg":"小弟之前係iOS 8 jailbreak過<br />\n升到iOS 10.3.1就已經冇搞過jailbreak既野了<br />\n但被其他apps好似銀行app block左<br />\n因為佢detect到我既device jailbroken<br />\n有冇巴打知個app係點樣分係咪jailbroken ?<br />\n我上網望過<br />\n我用ifunbox check 過device 入面冇<br />\n- /Applications/<a href=\"http://cydia.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcydia.app&d=6NkRw8bGVUbXH5PeR8OX0wRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4403e27a\" target=\"_blank\">http://cydia.app</a><br />\n- /Library/MobileSubstrate/MobileSubstrate.dylib<br />\n- /bin/bash<br />\n- /usr/sbin/sshd<br />\n- /etc/apt<br />\n- /private/var/lib/apt<br />\n- /private/jailbreak.txt<br />\n亦都打開唔到 cydia://package/com.example.package<br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81de9ef87d9a78a1207c710edec2c2c39d647c1c","tid":772601,"uid":8776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:12:25.000Z","msg":"係咪一直升，冇factory reset過？"},{"pid":"dc46f6976015d2fe1644edd9cd5ad6594de8ba4c","tid":772601,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81de9ef87d9a78a1207c710edec2c2c39d647c1c","tid":772601,"uid":8776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:12:25.000Z","msg":"係咪一直升，冇factory reset過？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:12:55.000Z","msg":"Jailbreak 變正版果時"},{"pid":"2ad7948c14c35e1bc8c2ae2c19120b9cc1641bdd","tid":772601,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"重裝啦"},{"pid":"0e8c6912bdb17db46559f66b4e9deb1059dfa788","tid":772601,"uid":6381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02: